DOCUMENT();

loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showpartialcorrectanswers = 1;

$a = non_zero_random(-12, 13, 1);
$b = non_zero_random(-8,7,1);
$c = random (2,6,1);
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Consider the function \(f(x)=e^{$c x} g(x) \) , where
\(g(0) = $a\) and   \( g'(0) = $b \).
$BR
Find \( f'(0) \).
$BR
\( f'(0) \) = \{ans_rule(30) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $c*$a+$b;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();
